{"id":232346163,"title":"嘗試減塑～其實比想像中還要簡單👌","content":"以下真實經驗👉\n今年大概夏天開始，整個有點迷上叫外送\n各種外送平台app都太方便\n尤其我外宿，幾乎整個週末都可以不出門😳\n但也發現每次餐盒餐碗塑膠袋垃圾非常多\n\n上上週國慶返家媽媽給了我一個便當餐袋\n她說是從屈臣氏集點換購到的\n除了餐袋本身，裡面還有玻璃保鮮盒與餐具\nhttps://i.imgur.com/i8Utlma.jpg\nhttps://i.imgur.com/QpLMyew.jpg\n\n原本還有一點彆扭…但這幾天我開始會帶出門\n像是中午下課後去外帶八方的水餃，店員滿友善😂\n我額外加點燙青菜，也有請他們直接放一起\n袋子本身有保溫效果，帶回家邊享用邊看youtube也很👌\n\n雖然只是一個初心者\n但發現嘗試減塑一點都不困難 \n希望我起步不算晚，下一步想帶飲料杯去買手搖飲‼️‼️","excerpt":"以下真實經驗，今年大概夏天開始，整個有點迷上叫外送，各種外送平台app都太方便，尤其我外宿，幾乎整個週末都可以不出門，但也發現每次餐盒餐碗塑膠袋垃圾非常多，上上週國慶返家媽媽給了我一個便當餐袋，她說是","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"49eed176-a7ad-492c-b6cf-77733ab633ef","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-10-21T16:08:10.830Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-21T16:08:10.830Z","commentCount":10,"likeCount":161,"tags":[],"topics":["環保","無痕"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"無痕生活","forumAlias":"ecolife","school":"國立政治大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":161}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/i8Utlma.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/QpLMyew.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"9940a2e7-5017-44f8-93ce-3971e56789b1","url":"https://i.imgur.com/i8Utlmal.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/i8Utlmal.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/i8Utlmal.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-21T16:08:10.830Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-21T16:08:10.830Z"},{"id":"9940a2e7-5017-44f8-93ce-3971e56789b1","url":"https://i.imgur.com/i8Utlma.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/i8Utlma","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/i8Utlmal.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-21T16:08:10.830Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-21T16:08:10.830Z"},{"id":"c41d258c-b0b8-47af-b37d-721